@gateway = http://localhost:8080
@tenant = northstar-agency
@policyId = 20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@fieldId = 30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### Policy as producer
GET {{gateway}}/api/policies/{{policyId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}
X-Actor-Id: producer-1001
X-Actor-Name: Jordan Miller
X-Role: Producer

### Report a loss as producer
POST {{gateway}}/api/claims
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}
X-Actor-Id: producer-1001
X-Actor-Name: Jordan Miller
X-Role: Producer

{
  "policyId": "{{policyId}}",
  "fieldId": "{{fieldId}}",
  "lossDate": "2026-06-12",
  "lossCause": "Hail",
  "description": "Hail damage observed across the northern field."
}

### List claims as reviewer
GET {{gateway}}/api/claims
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}
X-Actor-Id: reviewer-4001
X-Actor-Name: Casey Patel
X-Role: ClaimsReviewer

### Operations dashboard
GET {{gateway}}/api/operations/dashboard
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}
X-Actor-Id: ops-5001
X-Actor-Name: Riley Chen
X-Role: Operations
